/PL127/XXALEYNU/XX/PR

* */PR

And then all that has divided us will merge/PR

And then compassion will be wedded to power/PR

And then softness will come to a world that is harsh and unkind/PR

And then both men and women will be gentle/PR

And then both women and men will be strong/PR

And then no person will be subject to anotheròs will/PR

And then all will be rich and free and varied/PR

And then the greed of some will give way to the needs of many/PR

And then all will share equally in the Earthòs abundance/PR

And then all will care for the sick and the weak and the old/PR

And then all will nourish the young/PR

And then all will cherish lifeòs creatures/PR

And then all will live in harmony with each other and the Earth/PR

And then everywhere will be called Eden once again./PR

Judy Chicago/XX/PR

